<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">There is a second book entitled &quot;No Time to Wave Goodbye&quot;, which was written in 2009.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">There is a second book entitled "No Time to Wave Goodbye", which was written in 2009.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
