<span id="freeTextContainer10321266134015627635">4.5 stars<br/><br/>I actually read this book 15 years ago when I was pregnant with my daughter. It has stayed with me all these years. I thought it was a great book. Depressing and sad given the subject but very well written and easy to read. I read it very quickly over a couple of days. <br/><br/> </span>

